"description" = "Open your mouth and cute germs pop up near your lips! Scrub back and forth and they run away. A playful AR tooth-brushing app designed for children aged 0–5.\n\nNo complicated controls. Just tap the big Start button in the middle of the screen and brushing time begins as a fun little game.\n\nFun moments:\n- Open your mouth and adorable germs appear around your lips\n- Wiggle a toothbrush or your hand back and forth to scare the germs away\n- Gentle sound effects turn brushing into a joyful event\n- Tap the Done button for a sparkly reward animation\n\nKeeps kids engaged:\nSurprise characters like bunnies, dogs, cats, rice balls, bread, stars and apples appear at random. There's always something new.\n\nFor parents:\n- Works the same way on both iPhone and iPad\n- Minimal text with a layout that's instantly clear to children\n- Bright, playful colors and friendly germs\n\nTurn daily tooth-brushing from a chore into a fun moment with Germ Buster AR.";
"keywords" = "tooth brushing,kids,toddler,AR,parenting,teeth,germs,children,preschool";
"supportUrl" = "https://rork.com/support";
